      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

<script>
 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });
    //]]>

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

<script>
 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

<script>
 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });
    //]]>
</script>

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

<script>
 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });

      <script>
       /** Workaround without refactoring theme due to disabling Wyomind Elasticsearch **/
    require(['jquery','matchMedia'], function ($, matchMedia) {

        matchMedia({
            media: '(min-width: 960px)',
            entry: function () {
                $("#search").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search2').val($('#search').val());
                });
            },
            exit: function (e) {

                $(".block-mobile-search-trigger .form.minisearch .label").on('click touchend', function(event) {
                    event.stopPropagation();
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $('.form.minisearch').toggleClass('active');
                });

                $("#search2").on('input',function(e) {
                    $('#search').val($('#search2').val());
                });

            }
        });
    });
      </script>

<script>
 //<![CDATA[
    require([
        'jquery',
        'amShopbyAjax',
        'domReady!'
    ], function ($) {
        'use strict';

        window.hiderProcess = function () {
            $('.tocart').each(function (i, addToCartBtn) {
                let btn = $(addToCartBtn);

                                    btn.addClass('login-to-see-trade-prices');
                    btn.prop('type', 'button');

                    btn.click(function () {
                        location.href = 'https://trade.warcradle.com/customer/account/login/';
                    });

                    btn.find('span').text('Login to See Trade Prices');
                
                btn.show();
            });

                    }
        hiderProcess();

        $.widget('mage.amShopbyAjax', $.mage.amShopbyAjax, {
            reloadHtml: function (data) {
                this._super(data);
                hiderProcess();
            }
        });
    });
    //]]>
</script>
